<topic topic-id="DDeviceBaystabVLANconfiguration" xmlns:fn="http://www.w3.org/2005/02/xpath-functions">
  <title>Device Bays tab</title>
  <source>/120814-042457/Help/en/topics/DDeviceBaystabVLANconfiguration.xml</source>
  <keywords>VLAN membership device bays</keywords>
  <intro />
  <sections>
    <section>
      <desc />
      <content>
        <p class="bodytext">This screen displays the VLAN membership of each device bay in the enclosure and enables you to change the membership. All multi-blade servers must be on the same VLAN.</p>
        <p class="bodytext">To change the membership of a device bay, select a defined VLAN from the menu under the VLAN column, and click <b>Apply.</b></p>
        <p class="alertspacerbefore" />
        <table width="100%" style="border-collapse:collapse;" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2" rowsep="0" colsep="0">
