            </td>
            <td style="border-top:1px solid #0066FF;border-right:0px;border-bottom:1px solid #0066FF;border-left:0px;" align="left">
              <p class="tablebodytext">
                <b style="color:#0066FF;">NOTE:</b>  Accessing the Active OA through a link-local IPv6 address might not work on all client system setups containing multiple network interfaces.
</p>
